{"tid":1172164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「Toyota在哪？」川普與日企餐敘 調侃豐田社長","createTime":"2019-05-26T08:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T05:37:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":91,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bb2aa7859db3da711f0deaa2a6999ebcc87a3f","tid":1172164,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/05/26/phpJs2pYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F05%2F26%2FphpJs2pYc.jpg&h=ac6364d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n川普在餐敘中大力調侃豐田社長，顯然有注意到之前豐田的聲明。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普從昨（25）日開始進行為期4日的國是訪問，昨晚先在美國大使館與日本商界高層餐敘，期間除了表明希望日企能加大投資美國外，也大開豐田（Toyota）老闆的玩笑，反映了之前Toyota強烈措詞聲明的餘波。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報導，昨晚的餐敘中，川普向眾人問道：「豐田（Toyota）在哪？」而當眾人指出了豐田社長豐田章男後，川普稱：「一點都不像老闆阿！我以為另外那位才是你呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/05/26/phpjJb2Q0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F05%2F26%2FphpjJb2Q0.jpg&h=141d7f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豐田社長豐田章男。（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n川普與豐田的插曲，歸因於川普過去以來，就一直批評對日本的鉅額貿易逆差，尤其特別點名汽車業是美國的「國安威脅」。而作為日本企業，Toyota非常罕見地發表聲明 稱，豐田大力投資美國60年，雇用數十萬計員工，對美國經濟有重大貢獻，而川普的言論反應了美國不歡迎他們的投資，也不重視豐田的美國員工。<br />\n<br />\n而在昨晚雖然川普也提到日本在美國的「巨大優勢」，不過稱「這無所謂，也許這是你們為什麼這麼喜歡我們的原因」，還稱與會者都是「世界上最偉大的男女商人們」，是「美國無比美好的投資者」，不過他也表明希望這些日企投資美國的力度繼續加大。<br />\n<br />\n而川普也在會中談到日美貿易協議，稱希望能夠達成促進貿易平衡，並且確保公平及互惠的協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2802566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2802566&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BUBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=95e203f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2802566&h=87c385a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2802566</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-05-25/trump-dines-with-japan-executives-including-one-who-rebuked-him\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-05-25%2Ftrump-dines-with-japan-executives-including-one-who-rebuked-him&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BUBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=b5a59f99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-05-25/trump-dines-with-japan-executives-including-one-who-rebuked-him</a>"},{"pid":"f86314a06a1858f3f9e24bd2a0a167f54906a13d","tid":1172164,"uid":52215,"like":83,"dislike":42,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"傻閪侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16aabd4d5b09ead8c5055f493220827ec763e9eb","tid":1172164,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd6a62d3c9a26ce154d8115bfee2b1c10d2f0a7","tid":1172164,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56c244c3a1a67fb7433aee1efc29f96ed2f1581","tid":1172164,"uid":168784,"like":208,"dislike":0,"score":208,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"佢好鐘意挑人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試人低線"},{"pid":"81724f7856c6b5a4228e64bfc29e3f11082c1cbf","tid":1172164,"uid":168784,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"b56c244c3a1a67fb7433aee1efc29f96ed2f1581","tid":1172164,"uid":168784,"like":208,"dislike":0,"score":208,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"佢好鐘意挑人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試人低線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"底